Suggested by the Japanese stylist

00:05:33.940 --> 00:05:37.540
I never had haircut like this, never had so long done hairstyle.

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.900
I never had perm.

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:44.080
And for me the stylist never arranged every hair individually.

